*epm-0.8.8 (28 Apr 2004)

  28 Apr 2004; Aron Griffis <agriffis@gentoo.org> -epm-0.7.ebuild,
  -epm-0.8.1.ebuild, -epm-0.8.2.ebuild, -epm-0.8.3.ebuild, -epm-0.8.4.ebuild,
